description:
It took a little coaxing to get Jaden out of his shell.

He's a bit on the reserved side, and he responded to most of our questions with a cute, shy smile.

"I'm the guy next door I guess," he said when asked to describe himself. "I like to play baseball and I'm learning to surf."

"So are you shy around girls, too?" I asked.

"Sometimes," he said. "It depends on the girl. The prettier they are the more shy I get..."

Jaden is in school now and hopes to graduate next year!
title: Jaden
